				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Nice timing, I just fixed a bug related to simultaneous NMI and BRK that caused Dragon Warrior III to rarely crash on screen transitions. Very annoying in the sense that it could only be reproduced by walking up and down staircases for 5 minutes.
<br />
<br />Anyway, The BRK interrupt gets totally ignored if an IRQ or NMI occurs at the same time.
<br />If an NMI and IRQ occur at the same time, NMI has priority, and the IRQ will occur after the I bit gets reset again (or not at all if the IRQ line gets acknowledged before that happens). *edit* er, yeah, what Bregalad said <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /></div>

